main event: Reports of a UFO sighting in Englishtown, New Jersey, on November 27, 1957.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 20 minutes,The object appeared as a shining star,The object moved erratically, including hovering, descending, and ascending,The object emitted a light that appeared to be flashing,Initial observations indicate that the total sighting time was 2 hours and 15 minutes.
witness description: The document does not indicate confirmed witnesses, only records of the sighting.
